About the page
    congratulation page is designed to notify the fitwell app user that they have successfully created an account with the fitwell web application.

content of page
    1. hero image of man
    2. button with "Go to Dashboard" call action
    3. text1/action: Congratulations.
    Your account has been set up
    successfully
    4. text2/comment: You’re Doing Well!
    5. aesthetic pattern (svg)

